  "title": "Regulatory Compliance Analyst – Gap Analysis (6 months contract, convertible)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Regulatory Compliance Analyst – Gap Analysis </strong></p><p>We are supporting a leading life insurer in the search for a Regulatory Compliance professional to support a 6-month contract focused on regulatory gap analysis. This contract is convertible for high performers. </p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conduct regulatory gap analysis against MAS and LIA requirements</p></li><li><p>Review existing policies, procedures, and controls to identify gaps</p></li><li><p>Support remediation plans and work with internal stakeholders to address findings</p></li><li><p>Assist with documentation and regulatory readiness initiatives</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>3–6 years of experience in Regulatory Compliance within life insurance</li><li><p>Strong knowledge of MAS and LIA regulations</p></li></ul><p><ul><li>Hands-on experience with gap analysis or regulatory reviews</li></ul></p><p><p>Company Reg No.: 201131609D | License No.: 24S2411 | Reg No: R24121689 | Desiree Low Sher Rae</p></p>",
